#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:1 of
msgid "Compute the N-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform for real input."
msgstr "计算实数输入的 N 维离散傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the N-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform over "
"any number of axes in an M-dimensional real tensor by means of the Fast "
"Fourier Transform (FFT).  By default, all axes are transformed, with the "
"real transform performed over the last axis, while the remaining "
"transforms are complex."
msgstr ""
"该函数通过快速傅里叶变换（FFT）计算 M 维实数张量中任意数量轴上的 N 维离散"
"傅里叶变换。默认情况下，所有轴都会被变换，实数变换在最后一个轴上执行，"
"其余变换为复数变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:9 of
msgid "Input tensor, taken to be real."
msgstr "输入张量，视为实数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:11 of
msgid ""
"Shape (length along each transformed axis) to use from the input. "
"(``s[0]`` refers to axis 0, ``s[1]`` to axis 1, etc.). The final element "
"of `s` corresponds to `n` for ``rfft(x, n)``, while for the remaining "
"axes, it corresponds to `n` for ``fft(x, n)``. Along any axis, if the "
"given shape is smaller than that of the input, the input is cropped.  If "
"it is larger, the input is padded with zeros. if `s` is not given, the "
"shape of the input along the axes specified by `axes` is used."
msgstr ""
"从输入中使用的形状（每个变换轴的长度）。（``s[0]`` 表示轴 0，``s[1]`` "
"表示轴 1，依此类推）。`s` 的最后一个元素对应 ``rfft(x, n)`` 中的 `n`，而"
"其余轴对应 ``fft(x, n)`` 中的 `n`。在任意轴上，如果给定的形状小于输入，则"
"对输入进行裁剪；如果大于输入，则用零填充。如果未提供 `s`，则使用输入在 `"
"axes` 指定轴上的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:20 of
msgid ""
"Axes over which to compute the FFT.  If not given, the last ``len(s)`` "
"axes are used, or all axes if `s` is also not specified."
msgstr ""
"用于计算 FFT 的轴。如果未提供，则使用最后 ``len(s)`` 个轴，或者如果 `s` "
"也未指定，则使用所有轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:23 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:26 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axes"
" indicated by `axes`, or by a combination of `s` and `a`, as explained in"
" the parameters section above. The length of the last axis transformed "
"will be ``s[-1]//2+1``, while the remaining transformed axes will have "
"lengths according to `s`, or unchanged from the input."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，沿 `axes` 指定的轴变换，或由 `s` 和 `a` "
"的组合决定，如上参数部分所述。最后一个变换轴的长度将是 ``s[-1]//2+1``，"
"其余变换轴的长度根据 `s` 确定，或与输入保持不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:34 of
msgid "If `s` and `axes` have different length."
msgstr "如果 `s` 和 `axes` 的长度不同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:35 of
msgid "If an element of `axes` is larger than than the number of axes of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axes` 中的某个元素大于 `a` 的轴数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`irfftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:40 of
msgid ""
"The inverse of `rfftn`, i.e. the inverse of the n-dimensional FFT of real"
" input."
msgstr "`rfftn` 的逆变换，即实数输入的 N 维 FFT 的逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:43 of
msgid "The one-dimensional FFT, with definitions and conventions used."
msgstr "一维 FFT，包含所使用的定义和约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:45 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rfft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:46 of
msgid "The one-dimensional FFT of real input."
msgstr "实数输入的一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:49 of
msgid "The n-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "N 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:51 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rfft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:52 of
msgid "The two-dimensional FFT of real input."
msgstr "实数输入的二维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:55 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:56 of
msgid ""
"The transform for real input is performed over the last transformation "
"axis, as by `rfft`, then the transform over the remaining axes is "
"performed as by `fftn`.  The order of the output is as for `rfft` for the"
" final transformation axis, and as for `fftn` for the remaining "
"transformation axes."
msgstr ""
"对于实数输入，变换在最后一个变换轴上执行，如 `rfft` 所示，然后对剩余轴"
"执行变换，如 `fftn` 所示。输出的顺序对于最后一个变换轴与 `rfft` 相同，"
"对于其余变换轴与 `fftn` 相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfftn.rfftn:62 of
msgid "See `fft` for details, definitions and conventions used."
msgstr "有关详细信息、定义和所使用的约定，请参见 `fft`。"

